OL,3,CMigrants risk it all as US political
OL,4,Cdivide on Texas-Mexico border widens
OL,6,FYet, this is precisely the country the
OL,7,Ftwo old men vying for the presidency -
OL,8,FUS President Joe Biden and former
OL,9,FPresident Donald Trump - chose to
OL,10,Fvisit, knowing that immigration is now
OL,11,Fthe number one concern for American
OL,12,Fvoters ahead of the election,
OL,13,Faccording to recent polling.
OL,15,FThe crumbling buildings and barren
OL,16,Flandscape of Sanderson look familiar
OL,17,Fto those who love Westerns or Cohen
OL,18,FBrothers thrillers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/14
