OL,6,FThis isn't remote by Texas standards.
OL,7,FBut as they say, in the Lone Star
OL,8,Fstate everything is bigger here and
OL,9,Fthat holds for distances too.
OL,11,FSanderson is surrounded by mile after
OL,12,Fmile of desolate and beautiful scrub.
OL,13,FIt's also within sight of the Mexican
OL,14,Fborder.
OL,16,FHere, frontier politics feel very real.
OL,18,FThis tiny community of 694 people is
OL,19,Fon the frontline of what Trump has
OL,20,Flikened to a war.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
