OL,6,FSheriff Thaddeus Cleveland is just one
OL,7,Fline of defense in the battle to stop
OL,8,Fillegal crossings.
OL,10,FHe showed ITV News around his vast
OL,11,Fpatch and points out where migrants
OL,12,Ffrequently hide, waiting for their
OL,13,Fsmugglers to pick them up and take
OL,14,Fthem north.
OL,16,FHe exudes southern charm, adding "sir"
OL,17,Fto the end of every response. But he
OL,18,Fis steely in his resolve to catch
OL,19,Fthose trying to enter the United
OL,20,FStates illegally.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
