OL,6,FMr Cleveland is a fan of Trump,
OL,7,Frecently taking part in the former
OL,8,FPresident's motorcade during a
OL,9,Fcampaign visit.
OL,11,FHe firmly believes that under Biden,
OL,12,Fborder security has been seriously
OL,13,Feroded.
OL,15,FOfficial statistics bear out his
OL,16,Fdisapproval to some degree.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/14
