OL,6,FIt's projected that under Biden's
OL,7,Fpresidency, eight million people will
OL,8,Fhave crossed into the US illegally -
OL,9,Ffar more than under Trump, Obama or
OL,10,FBush.
OL,12,FDemocrats point out they are trying to
OL,13,Ftake measures to alleviate the
OL,14,Fsituation, but face Republican
OL,15,Fresistance.
OL,17,FBesides, some argue America
OL,18,Fdesperately needs migrants to bolster
OL,19,Fthe workforce as the economy continues
OL,20,Fto recover.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/14
