OL,12,Fwere cut like Asylum Cooperative
OL,13,FAgreements with countries like
OL,14,FHonduras and Guatemala.
OL,16,FThese policies forced asylum seekers
OL,17,Fto go back to their country of origin
OL,18,Fto claim asylum in the US.
