OL,6,FThe arguments about the cruelty of
OL,7,Fthese policies still range, but there
OL,8,Fis a consensus emerging that the
OL,9,Fcurrent situation on the US border is
OL,10,Funtenable.
OL,12,FDemocrats point out they had thrashed
OL,13,Fout a bipartisan deal in the Senate,
OL,14,Fto funnel extra cash for border
OL,15,Fsecurity to key agencies, but this was
OL,16,Ftorpedoed by Trump, who they claim
OL,17,Fwants to perpetuate the border chaos.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
