OL,6,FThey accuse him and his House of
OL,7,FRepresentatives Leader Mike Johnson of
OL,8,Fdeliberately killing off the plan for
OL,9,Fcynical political motives, hoping to
OL,10,Fcontinue the crisis until the eve of
OL,11,Fthe election.
OL,13,FCaught in the middle of all this
OL,14,Fmaneuvering, are the genuine asylum
OL,15,Fseekers who are fleeing violence or
OL,16,Frepression in their home countries.
OL,18,FWe met some at a migrant reception
OL,19,Fcentre in the border town of Eagle
OL,20,FPass.
