OL,4,Cdivide on Texas-Mexico border widens
OL,6,FRolando Penafiel had walked with his
OL,7,Fwife and two children thousands of
OL,8,Fmiles from Ecuador to escape cartel
OL,9,Fdeath squads.
OL,11,FThe gangs had already sprayed his home
OL,12,Fwith bullets after he refused to hand
OL,13,Fover profits from his construction
OL,14,Fbusiness.
OL,16,FHis daughter's feet were covered in
OL,17,Fangry-looking blisters, her legs
OL,18,Flacerated with scratches from miles of
OL,19,Ftraipsing through the cactus-filled
OL,20,Fdesert.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/14
