OL,6,FElsewhere, we saw a man who had just
OL,7,Fswum over, looking for a way through
OL,8,Fthe fence.
OL,10,FThese were pitiful scenes. All
OL,11,Fstriving for a better life, all
OL,12,Frisking their lives to get it.
